igner-goes-on-trial-1.1068937 |accessdate=2012-09-01 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20120902003017/http://gulfnews.com/news/gulf/saudi-arabia/saudi-campaigner-goes-on-trial-1.1068937 |archivedate=2012-09-02}}</ref>\n<ref name=\"BBC_10to30k\">{{cite news |first=Sue Lloyd |last=Roberts |pages= |title=Saudi Arabia show of force stifles 'day of rage' protests |date=2011-03-11 |publisher=BBC |url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/2/hi/programmes/newsnight/9422550.stm |accessdate=2012-09-02 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20120906000312/http://news.bbc.co.uk/2/hi/programmes/newsnight/9422550.stm |archivedate=2012-09-06}}</ref>\n\n<!-- CDHRAP -->\n<ref name=\"WISER_CDHRAP_NGO\">{{cite web|author1=World Index of Social |author2=Environmental Responsibility |authorlink=WiserEarth |title=Committee for the Defense of Human Rights in the Arabian Peninsula CDHRAP |language=French |publisher=[[WiserEarth]] |date=2006-01-18 |url=http://fr.wiserearth.org/organization/view/9199489bcfdeb80f04933a85e75f434e |format= |doi= |accessdate=2012-01-12 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20160106231728/http://fr.wiserearth.org/organization/view/9199489bcfdeb80f04933a85e75f434e |archivedate=2016-01-06}}</ref>\n<ref name=\"ColumbiaLawSchool_CDHRAP\">{{cite web |last=Arthur W. Diamond Law Library |title=Middle East organizations and web resources |publisher=[[Columbia Law School]] |year=2008 |url=http://www.hrcr.org/regional/middle.html |doi= |accessdate=2012-01-12 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20120316195212/http://www.hrcr.org/regional/middle.html |archivedate=2012-03-16}}</ref>\n\n<!-- ACPRA -->\n<ref name=\"AI_2012_charges\">{{cite web |title=Saudi Arabia ramps up clampdown on human rights activists |publisher=[[Amnesty International]] |date=2012-06-18 |url=https://www.amnesty.org/en/news/saudi-arabia-ramps-clampdown-human-rights-activists-2012-06-18 |format= |doi= |accessdate=2012-07-20 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20120802015219/http://www.amnesty.org/en/news/